{"tid":585138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 同英國一樣咁on9","createTime":"2018-03-08T11:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T12:08:45.000Z","uid":7109,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d334d637e80b0fd279527f95cc86afa7b6e260","tid":585138,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:40:52.000Z","msg":"成個iCloud / 香港交俾中國，然後由得iCloud / 香港腐敗落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5089634c2f9e8d0ca568e444e9f01e40457510","tid":585138,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:42:27.000Z","msg":"蘋果因應中國政府的相關規定，在上月28日正式將其iCloud運營業務轉交人月內地的「雲上貴州」公司營運，豈料首日就傳出有客戶個人資料失竊事件！有網友在發微博發文指，有蘋果技術支援人員利用職務之便，入侵其iCloud賬戶，非法獲取他的隱私資料用作敲詐勒索。蘋果公司昨早已和其聯絡，稱該涉事員工已被開除，但拒絕透露詳情。當事人惟有報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n員工疑改密碼勒索用家<br />\n<br />\n據涉事網友「美國往事1999」表示，事發上月28日下午3時55分，他致電蘋果客服熱線查詢有關iCloud相關事宜，但是接聽的一名技術支援人員態度敷衍，兩人因而在電話裏發生口角。<br />\n結束通話後，該名員工更回電騷擾和辱罵他。晚上9時56分，該名員工又用一個陝西西安註冊的手機打給他，直接道明身份，並表示要利用職務之便入侵了他的iCloud，複製所有訊息和資料，還威脅他要加當時人的QQ，否則會公開其個人訊息。<br />\n涉事網友其後發現，自己多個郵箱密碼已經被人修改，無法登入，幾經操作才恢復過來，之後收一封恐嚇電郵。由於iCloud裏面存儲了許多個人訊息和資料，以及金融賬戶的密碼，當時人對此感到擔憂。事後，他多次向蘋果客服反映，直到第三天才有一名女經理跟進事件。<br />\n雖然蘋果曾經承諾，中國iCloud將會設立嚴密的資料私隱及安全保護機制，亦不會在系統中設置後門，但雲上貴州有權存取iCloud中的所有資料，更有與蘋果共用、交換和披露所有用戶資料的權利，因此無國界記者組織早前的憂慮，不無道理。<br />\n微 博"},{"pid":"7eeb6a604a052b9138a0d1e6e280ac5703e8bedd","tid":585138,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:42:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180308/20325702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F20325702&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=c2e1b4a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F20325702&h=645e1ba1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180308/20325702</a>"},{"pid":"e4c1982689f44f14f32841664afd8f6a0b2e05f3","tid":585138,"uid":43042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"Apple賺到笑=on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ed6850d68145b8ff9bb2a7fd4e5b55e4d12f53","tid":585138,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c1982689f44f14f32841664afd8f6a0b2e05f3","tid":585138,"uid":43042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"Apple賺到笑=on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"你又啱wo"},{"pid":"fc26685da6171e944e45ddb3962057edef432f02","tid":585138,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:53:20.000Z","msg":"你就on9,英國奉旨養你一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心態衰過支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df3ed4aaef3d04c5e54ef78ee6a7c0b088e5b19","tid":585138,"uid":151286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"英國同香港有親咩？佢黎香港主要咪都係為搵錢，你估佢做善事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中國要收翻香港，唔同英國會為香港而得罪中國咩"},{"pid":"fafe8a71b86413342a443afa5f21203379e2c3f9","tid":585138,"uid":151286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df3ed4aaef3d04c5e54ef78ee6a7c0b088e5b19","tid":585138,"uid":151286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"英國同香港有親咩？佢黎香港主要咪都係為搵錢，你估佢做善事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中國要收翻香港，唔同英國會為香港而得罪中國咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"唔通*"},{"pid":"69fea8bd38c14089b80cd1ac2fdc80693c31b01f","tid":585138,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"